Class DataSetTester

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ccc.deeplearning.base.DeepLearningTest
      • com.ccc.deeplearning.eval.DataSetTester

  • public class DataSetTester
extends DeepLearningTest
    DataSet runner main class. Basic idea is to feed it an algorithm, dataset, and the number of examples to use. It will then print out f1 scores for each dataset. Note that I need to add WAY more for tuning this yet as far as command line options go.

    Adam Gibson
